                    A Simple Blog by Flask
                    
Description:
A simple blog written by python & bootstrap.

Features:
1.With elasticsearch for blog search. Use ik and ik_smart for word segmentation.
2.With mongodb for blog storage and picture storage.

Environment:
python 2.7
mongodb 3.2
elasticsearch 2.2.1

How to run:
1.start es: ./bin/elasticsearch
2.start mongodb: ./bin/mongod.exe
3.start server: python run.py runserver -h 0.0.0.0 -p 5000
